    p Determines the maximum number of options that can be selected on the option picker that are sourced from a #[code &lt;select multiple&gt;] element. It has a default value set to #[code Infinity]. If the source element is an #[code &lt;input&gt;] element, then its default value will be #[code 1]. This means that the multiple selection feature will apply only to #[code &lt;select&gt;] element.
